      "details": {
        "message_id": "1484447578215944283",
        "channel_id": "1484447542983917680",
        "channel_name": "\u2b50 dop-map-tester-levels",
        "content": "\u269c **STAFF LEVELS & PAY STRUCTURE** \u269c\n\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\n\nYour level determines your pay. No exceptions. No negotiations.\nThe more you put in, the more you earn. It is that simple.\n\n\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\n\n**\u3014 LEVEL 1 \u3015 Paid Tester** \ud83d\udd30\n> Base pay.\n> You are here, you are working, and you are getting paid for it.\n> This is the starting point. Where you go from here is entirely up to you.\n> <@821412756729233439> \n\n\n**\u3014 LEVEL 2 \u3015 Improving Tester** \ud83d\udccb\n> Pay increase unlocked.\n> Minus - 3 Skip points https://discord.com/channels/1041450125391835186/1484447854633287821/1484447951425241088\n> \u2726 You must still be doing everything from Level 1.\n> You show up with a good attitude. You take feedback on board. You are willing to learn and you are visibly getting better.\n> This level is not about being perfect \u2014 it is about proving you want to be.\n> <@767494211359473676>  \n> <@1441424672930398359> \n\n**\u3014 LEVEL 3 \u3015 Full Marker Tester** \ud83c\udfaf\n> Pay increase unlocked.\n> Minus - 5  Skip points https://discord.com/channels/1041450125391835186/1484447854633287821/1484447951425241088\n> \u2726 You must still be doing everything from Levels 1 and 2.\n> You complete all assigned markers on the day, every time.\n> No missing taks. No half-finished sessions. You do the task  in full and you do it consistently.\n> This is the standard every tester should be working toward.\n> <@1005758035723026444>\n> <@1250261619141775402>\n> <@871514657804931112>",
        "edited_at": "2026-06-01T14:10:43.057976+00:00",
